<figureCitation box="[481,583,1803,1830]" captionStart="FIGURE 57" captionStartId="117.[151,250,1605,1630]" captionTargetBox="[161,1427,491,1579]" captionTargetId="figure@117.[160,1427,489,1580]" captionTargetPageId="117" captionText="FIGURE 57. Corythalia spp., photographic images of male specimens, dorsal view. Corythalia latipes: A Neotype from Bahia, Brazil. Corythalia conferta sp. nov.: B Paratype M-1, IBSP 131451, from São Paulo, Brazil. Corythalia drepane sp. nov.: C Holotype from Amazonas, Brazil. Corythalia antepagmenti sp. nov.: D Paratype from Acre, Brazil. Corythalia ricti Bayer, sp. nov.: E Holotype from East Berbice-Corentyne, Guyana. Corythalia parva: F Lectotype from Brazil. Corythalia protensa sp. nov.: G Holotype from Amazonas, Brazil. Corythalia placata: H Male MCZ 20545-II (Paralectotype of Dynamius blandus) from Trinidad. Corythalia gasnieri sp. nov.: I Holotype from Amazonas, Brazil." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3927501" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3927501/files/figure.png" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">Fig. 57E</figureCitation>
). Opisthosoma like noted in genus description under general dorsal colouration, except for chevron-like patch in central band missing (
<figureCitation box="[820,922,1838,1865]" captionStart="FIGURE 57" captionStartId="117.[151,250,1605,1630]" captionTargetBox="[161,1427,491,1579]" captionTargetId="figure@117.[160,1427,489,1580]" captionTargetPageId="117" captionText="FIGURE 57. Corythalia spp., photographic images of male specimens, dorsal view. Corythalia latipes: A Neotype from Bahia, Brazil. Corythalia conferta sp. nov.: B Paratype M-1, IBSP 131451, from São Paulo, Brazil. Corythalia drepane sp. nov.: C Holotype from Amazonas, Brazil. Corythalia antepagmenti sp. nov.: D Paratype from Acre, Brazil. Corythalia ricti Bayer, sp. nov.: E Holotype from East Berbice-Corentyne, Guyana. Corythalia parva: F Lectotype from Brazil. Corythalia protensa sp. nov.: G Holotype from Amazonas, Brazil. Corythalia placata: H Male MCZ 20545-II (Paralectotype of Dynamius blandus) from Trinidad. Corythalia gasnieri sp. nov.: I Holotype from Amazonas, Brazil." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3927501" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3927501/files/figure.png" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">Fig. 57E</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
