<subSubSection pageId="31" pageNumber="32" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="31.[151,1437,1164,2043]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1910,1936]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">Remarks.</emphasis>
The short, relatively narrow, distally pointed embolus with prolateral direction and the relatively broad and short tegulum with a distinct proximal lobe exhibiting a prolateral lobe are similar to 
<taxonomicName authority="Bayer &amp; Höfer &amp; Metzner, 2020" authorityName="Bayer &amp; Höfer &amp; Metzner" authorityYear="2020" box="[1212,1396,1946,1972]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Corythalia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="31" pageNumber="32" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="antepagmenti" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[1212,1396,1946,1972]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">C. antepagmenti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">
<taxonomicNameLabel pageId="31" pageNumber="32" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Bayer &amp; Höfer &amp; Metzner, 2020" authorityName="Bayer &amp; Höfer &amp; Metzner" authorityYear="2020" box="[255,379,1981,2007]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Corythalia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="31" pageNumber="32" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="drepane" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[255,379,1981,2007]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">C. drepane</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[385,475,1981,2007]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[385,475,1981,2007]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
, so we expect a quite close relationship between these two species and 
<taxonomicName authority="Bayer" authorityName="Bayer" authorityYear="2020" box="[1277,1432,1981,2008]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Corythalia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="31" pageNumber="32" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ricti" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[1277,1357,1981,2007]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">C. ricti</emphasis>
Bayer
</taxonomicName>
, 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,241,2017,2043]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[151,241,2017,2043]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
